caption.title: Average number per branch of the different leaf and syconium phases.
caption.p: Young (A), mature (B) and senescent (C) female leaves and total female syconia (D); Young (F), mature (G) and senescent (H) male leaves and total male syconia (I) during the survey period; and the meteorological factors during the same period (E, J): September 2009 to August 2011.
